        + f"<div class='cost-detail-driver'>VOWD / Forecast: <b>{_html(vowd_ratio)}</b> | Exposure / Forecast: <b>{_html(exposure_ratio)}</b> | Cost check: <b>{_html(balanced)}</b></div>"
